      "sample_filtering_criteria": "Used TIMSS 2019 Grade 8 Science data. Curriculum type was operationalized from ITCOURSE: students with ITCOURSE=6 were classified as integrated science; students with ITCOURSE in {2,3,4,5} were classified as separated science. Variables were extracted and merged using IEA IDB Analyzer and SPSS; after data cleaning, 309,511 entries from 44 countries remained. For the dependent variable, all five plausible values (BSSSCI01–BSSSCI05) were used with separate analyses per PV. The manuscript states that Appendix A details missing-data procedures, and it reports that missing data were imputed prior to model training (including in the propensity-score estimation pipeline)."
    },
